    dc:description "Fig. 26. Corymorpha floridana n. spec (A) Holotype, BFLA4371, bell height 3 mm. (B) 01-APR-2019; photographed but not collected; mature male, 2 mm. (C) 11-MAR-2020; photographed but not collected; 2 mm. (D) BFLA4363; bell height 2 mm. (E) BFLA4362; 2 mm; note that part of the long tentacle and the entire intermediate length tentacle are missing." ;
